column5: Most of the bay has a skim of ice but there are still some open spots that all the divers are gathering at. Snow squalls in the forecast. I read recently that patience isn't how long you wait for something but how you wait.
it's the wind that will bugger it up
I can vouch for that,95% anyway frozen.Still a long way to go guys.The temps do look in our favor.
